latestIgtvVideos.caption:

📍So i broke my highlighter by mistake & this is one the best highlighter I’ve ever tried so had to fix it! This hack works on every powdered product such as bronzers, contours, blush and compacts! ✅

📍I have used Iso-propyl alcohol 99% . I would suggest you guys to use 70% rubbing alcohol. As the 70% was not available, i had to use this!

- Perfect for everyday use, pool days, or sunny outings🏖️
- Packed with SPF 50 PA++++, protects against blue light, and uses hybrid sunscreen filters🧴
- Leaves a non-greasy, velvety matte finish. 
- Soothes rather than irritates- amazing protection from sunburn and redness☀️
- Bonus: Doubles up as a primer for your makeup base🤌🏻
